Selenium Python Waits

why to use waits in Selenium?
- All elements in web page may not load at the same time
- Required for websites using Ajax and Javascript
- To avoid Elements Not Visible exception from selenium

What are implicit and Explicit waits?
- In selenium web driver it has 2 types of waits
- Implicit - Poll the DOM for a specific duration to locate an element 500ms until timeout ex -10 sec
- Explicit - waits for a certain condition to occur before proceeding with next step

How to use implicit wait and Explicit waits?
-